&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;样式:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background: grey; color: grey&#34;&gt;遮盖体-select&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;background: grey; color: grey&#34; onmouseout=&#34;this.style.background=&#39;grey&#39;;this.style.color=&#39;grey&#39;&#34; onmouseover=&#34;this.style=&#39;&#39;&#34;&gt;遮盖体-hove&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
